<h1 id='consumer-experience'>Consumer Experience</h1>
<p><strong>Note:</strong> The Candidate Consumer Experience (CX) Standards for Non-Bank Lending reflect the existing Banking Language Standards. Other sections of the CX Standards relating to data language not explicitly included on the Candidate Standards page including the <a href="https://consumerdatastandardsaustralia.github.io/standards/#data-language-standards-common">common data language standards</a>, <a href="https://consumerdatastandardsaustralia.github.io/standards/#customer-language-common">customer data language</a>, and <a href="https://consumerdatastandardsaustralia.github.io/standards/#profile-scope-and-standard-claims-common">profile scopes</a>, apply regardless of the sector.</p>
